OL,3,CCouncil passes motion labelling asylum
OL,4,Chotel riot a 'terrorist attack'
OL,6,FCouncillors in Rotherham have passed
OL,7,Fan official motion labelling the
OL,8,Frioting at a hotel in the town a
OL,9,F"terrorist attack".
OL,11,FViolence erupted outside the Holiday
OL,12,FInn Express, in Wath upon Dearne,
OL,13,Fduring an anti-immigration protest on
OL,14,F4 August.
OL,16,FThe hotel, which was housing around
OL,17,F200 asylum seekers at the time, had
OL,18,Fits windows smashed and missiles
OL,19,Fincluding wood, glass bottles and beer
OL,20,Fcans were thrown at officers.
